					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p195977">Please help consolidate all info for pixel artists for SNES</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=195977&amp;sid=9539cfe80f301ba98d5a361c9c298ba4#p195977"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed May 17, 2017 9:16 am&nbsp;</div></td>
